Why This Matters

This is the step that solves the "AI hallucination" problem from your project document. Because the AI agent (which we build tomorrow) will NEVER write its own SQL. It will only ask this Semantic Layer for numbers using safe, pre-defined measures. That means Finance and Sales will always see the exact same numbers — which is the whole point of MetricMind.
